summary: Completed comprehensive testing of AI Models Hub application. Backend API successfully fetches 412 models with proper categorization. Frontend displays models correctly with working tier/category filtering and navigation. All playgrounds load properly. API key management works. Chat and image generation APIs return expected error messages when no API key is provided (mocked behavior).
